//Command to use when deployment an app in the firebase//

1 - firebase login
2 - firebase init 
3 - From the list select : Hosting: Configure and deploy...
4 - Select: use an existing project 
5 - Select your project from the list
6 - On public directory write build
7 - follow the steps and respond yes or ( On github put no) no

8 - Bundle up the app and deploy it in the firebase 
// This command is run when the above command is already done at first time
9 - npm run build
10 - firebase deploy


// Apps to install to improve the development 

1 - Redux devTools
2 - React Developer Tools
